Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}Modern Shogi\NFamous Matches Chosen by\NShogi Players
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:01:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I really need to get curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The last piece of fried chicken...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's game is in the sixth block\Nof the Lion King tournament.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My opponent is Harunobu Nikaidou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's almost summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my first game after becoming\Na professional player.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.87,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,Harunobu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}When summer vacation hits,\Nshogi tournaments for children{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}are held on the roof of a department store.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before joining the federation,\Nstrong kids from around the country{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}participate in a number\Nof small tournaments like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Harunobu and I were regulars\Nat events like that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}so we'd already met many times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Children's\NShogi Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What grade was I in at that time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was terribly hot at that event,\Nand I was facing Harunobu in the semifinals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It really was hellishly hot that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He couldn't handle the heat well,\Nand was so flushed he looked like a red ogre,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and looked like he was in pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking at him made me feel terrible as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the afternoon, the wind died down,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}while the temperature kept climbing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think he was anemic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}His face was getting paler by the minute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an arrogant thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but I was looking\Nfor the shortest way to checkmate him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I should get the boy\Nsitting in front of me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}into a cool, air-conditioned room\Nas soon as possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...in the final stage,\Nas his imminent defeat became clear{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}he put every piece he had into his army,\Nand began a desperate act of resistance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A silent scream escaped\Nout of his sweaty, pale face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that moment,\NI was ashamed of my arrogance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The human sitting in front of me,\Ndrenched in sweat and reeling from the sun,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}was here because he wanted to win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I don't want to lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it was something that couldn't be helped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...it was going to be a long battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The victory was already mine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he struggled on, one move at a time,\Nsearching for a path that couldn't be found.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, he finally ran out of moves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how closely he looked,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}there was no path for his king to survive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}After muttering that, he began to shed\Ngreat big tears, just like in a manga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amid the crying of the cicadas\Nand the department store's background music,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I silently gazed at him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It would be the face I'd probably be\Nsitting across for decades to come.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Becoming a pro...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...is like jumping onto a moving train\Nthat doesn't stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can never get off of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not until you lose and fall off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this small universe,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's an endless cycle of winning and losing\Nuntil you start losing your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}As you gasp, "I don't want to lose".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go take a peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your rival is waiting for you\Nwith incredible spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}The calm mind is the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:50.84,RightSign,NTP,0,0,0,,CHUBBY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:50.84,LeftSign,NTP,0,0,0,,BOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He's giving off so much fighting spirit\Nthat it's like an entirely different manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's like, "Next chapter,\Nit's either checkmate or be checkmated!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I envy you, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:11.70,CenterSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,Excite\NExcite
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Look at that fighting spirit.\NThat's all for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}He said he was your lifelong rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, breathe in slowly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shallow breaths will narrow my field of vision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:35.26,EpNum,NTP,0,0,0,,CHUBBY\N(Actually, GRIN)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're late, Kiriyama!\NI got tired of waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I came at the appointed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're the one who arrived early, Nikaidou.\NGeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I guess my enthusiasm got the better of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}KNIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}2 - e - Knight. There it is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}2 - d - Silver General.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}3 - e - Pawn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Same, Silver General.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}1 - e - Pawn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's gotten stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's slowly but steadily attacking me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No good. I won't get anywhere\Nby just being on the defense.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to change the flow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}PAWN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sweat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same as that time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He looks pale.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something's wrong with Nikaidou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me, is the air conditioning working?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Something seems to be\Nwrong with it lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's okay, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's heaven compared to the roof\Nof that department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}LANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}5 - g - Lance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's coming in where I don't have pawns.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll do this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}7 - f - Pawn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Silver General
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}6 - h - Silver General?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Silver General
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Instead of taking gold, he moved silver?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to lose either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down. Take deep breaths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Expand your field of vision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I keep my composure,\Nthis board should be in my favor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down and keep playing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The game continued until evening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I continued to shake off\NHarunobu's tenacious attacks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't have a move. I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, that's right. This face...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It hasn't changed at all since we were kids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikaidou...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and me too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...will stay like this forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and ever and ever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Master Harunobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hanaoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SOUVENIR
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What about your vacation?\NWhat happened to traveling around the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought you weren't coming back\Nfor 80 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I had your mother take my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Thank you, Hanaoka!\NAre you sure it's okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ten days were plenty for me,\Nand it was a very satisfying trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'll be going, then!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To be honest, being separated from you\Nmade me worry a lot, Master Harunobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was in danger of having\Nan irregular heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}*Didn't refresh at all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You haven't gone to the hospital yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go see Dr. Morikawa right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've already called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you in pain, Master Harunobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your kidneys aren't functioning well again,\Nare they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry. While I was gone,\Nyou probably weren't eating well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hanaoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's all right. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Subsisting on hospital food alone\Nbuilds up stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And it's been this way since you were a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've seen how hard it's been for you\Nall of these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But it's all right, I'm here for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's take our time and get your health back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And with Mr. Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...how did the match go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't know how strong he'd gotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...I won't lose next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course, Master Harunobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:11.99,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,Harunobu
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:15.99,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,Beyond the Night Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}After my game with Nikaidou,\NI went to their house as promised.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Come over again after your match is over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}That's the last day of Obon,\Nso I'll make plenty of food.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good evening. It's Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's late. I bet you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You must be hungry. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry it took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Look, Momo. Rei is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I brought pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I knew you'd be late,\Nso I plated them separately for you, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a9}Downtown Specialty\NVarious Foods Triathlon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I know you have a small appetite,\Nso I put them in small portions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all looks delicious.\NBut I wonder if I can eat everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And this is for Grandma and Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I plated them using Momo's doll set.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}TINY...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}- What's that? What's that?\N- I want it, I want it, I want it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.65,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,GLARE GLARE\NGLARE GLARE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's so little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess two beers is too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ooph...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't sleep yet, Grandpa.\NWe have to light the ceremonial fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Already after nine? You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If it's too late, Grandma and your mom\Nwill have a hard time getting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The other day, you lit the fire in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's right. That was to welcome them home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We light that around dusk as if to say,\N"Hurry home. We're all waiting for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But when they go back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,we light the fire after dinner, saying,\N"We want you to stay as long as possible."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And when they come home, we put out\Ncucumber horses so they can get here faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But when they leave,\Nwe put out oxen made from eggplants
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so they can make a slow, safe return,\Nladen with the gifts we've given them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, shall we see them off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were all smiling as usual,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}but somehow a certain solemness\Npermeated the mood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seeing how they prepared horses and oxen...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Made a special feast...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Worrying with everyone\Nabout welcoming and sending off{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}the people who are no longer with us...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It just made me think of a sad ceremony\Nthat only brings back painful memories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Momo, let's take a bath and go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go to the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hina? Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you going to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, manga. I forgot a new issue is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go with her, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's walking fast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's she going?\NThe convenience store isn't that way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}There she is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't call out to her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her voice caused a lump in my throat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure she was holding it in\Nwhen she was with the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I'll go back in a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}As I listened to her sobbing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}the doubts I had shut away\Nbegan to seep into my heart like ink.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's stay here a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}For me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}For me, when I think about\Nthe real family I lost...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gave up on crying about it\Nbecause I thought it was pointless.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It made me sad to think about them,\Nso I tried not to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I chased them out of my head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I chased them out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chased them out...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...was that really the right thing to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.23,0:22:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}She's crying...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.94,0:22:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}...but I'm not.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}But the two of us are gazing up\Nat that beautiful,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}beautiful, beautiful July night sky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:01.04,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,Beyond the Night Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.01,0:24:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.01,0:24:38.14,EpNum,NTP,0,0,0,,Episode 4
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.43,0:24:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When you open it, it has to be like,\N"Wow! That's so cute!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.31,0:24:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hina is troubled with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.56,0:24:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, little one.\NI shall ask you your name. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.69,0:24:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bodoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.48,0:24:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your wonderful friend is just like\Na nice, round, shiny ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.11,0:24:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sis, you picked up another stranger?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.15,0:24:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't miss the next episode of\NMarch Comes in Like a Lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.99,0:24:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Study shogi with me, everyone!
